---
title: Beef, Bean & Mushroom Shepherd's Pie with Panko-Topped Mashed Potatoes
description: Shepherd’s pie is best known as a meaty, stick-to-your-ribs kind of dish. Our spin on this classic turns to mushrooms and creamy white beans for a vegan variation that’s equally hearty. Rounded out with peas, carrots, and a blanket of thyme-flecked mashed potatoes sprinkled with a crunchy golden panko topping, it’s a delicious mix of our favorite comforting flavors packed into one perfectly pleasing, ultra-savory pie.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64ad6e6508c61453c499aad0-96012e7a.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64aed096bf53a3eb58aab5fa.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/beef-bean-mushroom-shepherds-pie-64aed096bf53a3eb58aab5fa
time required: 40 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 1110 kcal
  fat: 53 g
  saturated fat: 13 g
  carbohydrates: 114 g
  sugar: 20 g
  protein: 45 g
  fiber: 18 g
  sodium: 1830 mg
servings: 2
cuisine: Irish
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
